Pre-Game Insights: Captain Jos Buttler will try to finalize his playing XI for T20 World Cup 2024 during this series.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The two teams will look forward to gaining momentum in this series before the T20 World Cup 2024 in West Indies and USA.
Others: England have a 19-9 lead in the T20I head-to-head record against Pakistan.
England lead by 7-4 in the head-to-head record between England and Pakistan on English soil.
England have won three out of their last five T20Is against Pakistan.
